name: /Clover/
description: Four-leafed clover is a solitary clover plant that has at least one four-leafed leaf, as opposed to the usual three-leafed leaf. In the Western tradition, it is believed that such a plant brings good fortune to the finder, especially if found by chance. Legend has it that each of the leaves of a quadruple leaf represents something specific: the first represents hope, the second faith, the third love, and the fourth good fortune.
